Third-party models and libraries used by videokit retain their own licenses
and are NOT covered by this notice:

- FFmpeg — LGPL / GPL (depending on build). https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html
- OpenAI Whisper — MIT. https://github.com/openai/whisper
- MediaPipe (BlazeFace .tflite) — Apache License 2.0. Downloaded at runtime
