- RNNoise model `cb.rnnn` — Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
  (CC-BY 4.0). https://github.com/GregorR/rnnoise-models. Downloaded at
  runtime; not redistributed by this repository.
- OpenCV — Apache License 2.0. https://opencv.org

These components keep their original licenses when used through videokit.
